TextBody:
Hello Jimmy,

Thank you for your response. The following is a summary of the ticket for your records.

Symptom
You were trying to run an FSAC scan where you were getting T2 DB file compression issues and g disk I/O error[0x030A] errors.

Resolution
Increasing the disc space and verifying the integrity of the physical hard disc will resolve the issue.

Following this email, you will receive an automated confirmation that the case is closed, along with the ability to re-open the case if any related errors return. In addition, you will also receive a separate email with a survey where you can let us know how we did. Feel free to leave any feedback via the survey link!

Have a great day!
